nodes.text: Octopi (singular octopus) were cephalopoids with eight tentacles.
At least one species of octopus was native to Naboo. The Gungan Jar Jar Binks once got one stuck to his head.
Arboreal octopi were native to Cholganna; Orion Ferret had a pet which might have belonged to this species. Dhol of Cheelit belonged to a race of sapient octopi.
